  <original-body>When using rake:migrate the schema.rb assumes for any case of integer :limit = nil a :limit =&gt; 11 default value and in this case my schemas from development and test db are different. This difference makes the int(11) columns be bigint(11) columns in the test db and this will deny the foreign key creation.</original-body>
